      dct:created "2026-03-19"^^xsd:date ;
      dct:description "Full-day strategic session between Scarlet Dame (founder) and Claude (AI coworker). Began as MVP/archetype interview, evolved into fundamental reframe of core value proposition, culminated in comprehensive strategy document. This memory captures key decisions made during document creation. Document lives at docs/strategy/strategy.md (8,500 words, 17 sections)." ;
