      skos:note "Three consultant use cases: (1) free modules as lead gen, (2) paid modules as content product (course/book substitute), (3) module as the consulting deliverable itself — instead of a deck, deliver a perspective the whole org can install. The deck is a derived artifact; the real value is the perspective shift. This is a major expansion of the consulting archetype." ;
      narr:theme "The consulting deliverable of the AI age is not a deck but an installable perspective module — the deck is a derived artifact" .

